{"tid":840893,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】澳洲悉尼、塔斯曼尼亞18日","createTime":"2018-09-29T07:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T22:42:19.000Z","uid":120678,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"95365e9a098c58cfc4c5bbfe5dc829bd1d9f3961","tid":840893,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:07:35.000Z","msg":"之前見到酷航兩千幾蚊連稅來回澳洲，心動之下買左飛飛澳洲，首先係去悉尼搵親戚玩下，兼且休息下長途機適應下時差，跟住然之後買左1800蚊左右維珍澳洲加Jetstar來回塔斯曼尼亞Hobart機票，計埋local tour成個trip唔駛八千蚊港幣。如果從香港跟團去塔斯曼尼亞冇兩萬都唔駛落樓<br />\n<br />\n塔斯曼尼亞搖籃山(Cradle Mountain)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/145032_c79f5efccb55137ff43e7597faddda77.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F145032_c79f5efccb55137ff43e7597faddda77.JPG&h=6d093085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/145353_4f1911179a8494f4e8c0f61da4ce9bc0.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F145353_4f1911179a8494f4e8c0f61da4ce9bc0.JPG&h=f755e079&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n塔斯曼尼亞列治文市老橋<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/145518_2c9168fd920df346af9c027c72cada19.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F145518_2c9168fd920df346af9c027c72cada19.JPG&h=7627a51a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n塔斯曼尼亞酒杯灣(Wineglass Bay)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/145626_bfa4cd7e5fd671de9a06c76ef63e3db4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F145626_bfa4cd7e5fd671de9a06c76ef63e3db4.JPG&h=e8e2c519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n悉尼海港大橋及歌劇院<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/145915_447b0997369d45207af293c5cf268a26.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F145915_447b0997369d45207af293c5cf268a26.JPG&h=db95f3fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/150129_a742bb2c80854f8a961cfdce46852094.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F150129_a742bb2c80854f8a961cfdce46852094.JPG&h=fc9f13c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n塔斯曼尼亞d海鮮真係好正，Hobart Fish 349餐廳一大個海鮮platter有魚有青口有生蠔有扇貝，加杯白葡萄酒for 3個人食到飽都係90蚊澳幣，重點係超好食"},{"pid":"3125aeec221b3557a4addd24a54db6492cda95e7","tid":840893,"uid":22243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:12:15.000Z","msg":"塔斯曼尼亞d海鮮真係好正，Hobart Fish 349餐廳一大個海鮮platter有魚有青口有生蠔有扇貝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解我全部都係炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3caa138ccdab466e2a75b50395158a3d94e4c4b","tid":840893,"uid":20639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:14:11.000Z","msg":"屌 我6月去塔斯曼尼亞嗰陣天氣又係唔撚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfdc4bd974fc4ffd11aa61778797807fb2a0ec3","tid":840893,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3caa138ccdab466e2a75b50395158a3d94e4c4b","tid":840893,"uid":20639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:14:11.000Z","msg":"屌 我6月去塔斯曼尼亞嗰陣天氣又係唔撚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:17:42.000Z","msg":"我去搖籃山天氣都係唔好呀，落足咁耐雨<br />\n連搖籃山既頂都響雲入面睇唔到"},{"pid":"769c30b108b101cf2fe646c455b7ea02cab275a7","tid":840893,"uid":20639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcfdc4bd974fc4ffd11aa61778797807fb2a0ec3","tid":840893,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3caa138ccdab466e2a75b50395158a3d94e4c4b","tid":840893,"uid":20639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:14:11.000Z"